<!-- Node: "Warcarft III Beta Patch v1.17 Released" -->
<div class="body_box_header">Warcarft III Beta Patch v1.17 Released</div>
<div class="body_box"><small>Submitted by <a href="http://www.gamedesign.net/user/view/76" title="View user profile.">RaVenous</a> on Sunday, August 15, 2004 - 18:45</small><br /><br />
A new beta patch (version 404) for Warcraft III v1.17 was released yesterday.  Users can log into the Westfall server on Battle.net to download the patch.  <br />
<br />
One of the biggest features included in the patch is two new neutral heroes.  More information about what the patch fixes and other new features added into the patch can be found <A HREF="http://www.battle.net/forums/war3/thread.aspx?fn=patch-beta&t=57610&p=1" ALT="Warcraft III Beta Patch Info">here</A>.
